00:08:40.620 --> 00:08:41.650
Ah ouais ? Trop fort !

00:08:48.370 --> 00:08:50.090
Mon dieu, ce drapeau...

00:08:51.250 --> 00:08:52.370
Des pirates !

00:08:54.420 --> 00:08:56.880
